I see all, Megan...

::Prowl::

Prowl continues to fly after Iron Raptor after hearing her words. He 
wasn't about to give up. Last time he let her leave his sight she got 
herself kidnapped!

"Look, love, at least let me come with you," he says, speeding up and 
swooping lower. If he could only get close enough....



--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, "Megan Solmonson" <tmrattrap@h...> wrote:
> Nothing gets past you, huh Yanshosh?
> 
> * There was just no escaping him was there? She was easily 
outdistencing 
> him...until she looked back and saw Prowl transform into beast mode.
> She growled, oh great! Now she bet he was going to try and stop her 
now.
> Even thought she knew that he was worried and it was very sweet, 
she still 
> wanted to find out just what had happened to her too.
> And with that, she changed course a bit and started heading for the 
forest 
> at the far end of the plain. Knowing that it could take her all the 
way to 
> the Ark, and if Prowl lost her in there then maybe he would go back 
to base 
> and stay there like she had ordered.
> But she growled.*
> 
> " I told you to stay back at base, now go!!"
> 
> * Basically calling over her shoulder.*
